## 📱 SECTION 2: MOBILE PLACEMENT MAP (React Native) - ./zarva-mobile

Every piece of mobile code has exactly one correct home.

| What you are building | Where it belongs |
| :--- | :--- |
| **New Screen** | `src/screens/{role}/{ScreenName}.jsx`. Register strictly in the corresponding Navigator (`CustomerNavigator`, `WorkerNavigator`, `AuthNavigator`). |
| **Reusable UI Component** | `src/components/{ComponentName}.jsx`. Zero business logic. Must be used across 2+ screens. |
| **Design Primitive (UI)** | `src/design-system/components/`. Buttons, Cards, Inputs. Receive props, render UI. Nothing else. |
| **Tokens / Theming** | `src/design-system/tokens.js`. NEVER hardcode Hex colors, spacing, or typography sizes in screens. |
| **Global State (Zustand)** | `src/stores/{domain}Store.js`. (e.g., `authStore`, `jobStore`, `workerStore`). Do not mix domains. |
| **API Call Functions** | `src/services/api/{domain}Api.js` or via `apiClient`. Screens call store actions, store actions call the API. |
| **Firebase References** | `src/services/FirebaseRealtime.js`. Keep all string paths localized here. |
| **Push Notifications** | `src/services/FCMService.js` and `NotificationHandler.js`. |
| **Device Location** | `src/services/LocationService.js`. Never invoke `expo-location` directly inside a UI screen. |
| **Pure Utility Logic** | `src/utils/{name}.js`. No side effects. No hooks. |
| **i18n Translations** | `src/i18n/translations/`. Always use `t('key')`. NEVER hardcode english text inside JSX. |

